<h2>Presentation</h2>
<p>Newton Adventure is a 2D platformer with a twist: the player can rotate gravity at 360&deg;.</p>
<p>Each level contains a key that must be brought to the exit door using Newton body to push it or the gravity power to make it fall. Gravity must also be used to avoid trap, kill enemy or solve puzzle.</p>
<p>The <strong>free</strong> base game provides 5 themed quests playable in any order for a total of 30 levels with various dexterity, exploration and reflexion gameplay flavor.</p>
<p>This game experience is extended by <i>pay what you want</i> mods.</p>
